[package]
name = "mas-http"
description = "HTTP utilities for the Matrix Authentication Service"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Quentin Gliech <quenting@element.io>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0"
homepage = "https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-authentication-service/"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service/"

[dependencies]
bytes = "1.5.0"
futures-util = "0.3.30"
headers = "0.3.9"
http-body = "0.4.5"
hyper = "0.14.27"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"

[features]
client = [ "dep:mas-tower", "dep:rustls", "hyper/tcp", "dep:hyper-rustls", "dep:rustls-platform-verifier", "tower/limit", "tower-http/timeout", "tower-http/follow-redirect", "tower-http/set-header",]

[lints.rust]
unsafe_code = "forbid"

[lints.clippy]
all = "deny"
pedantic = "warn"
str_to_string = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "deny"

[dependencies.http]
version = "0.2.11"

[dependencies.hyper-rustls]
optional = true
version = "0.25.0"
features = [ "http1", "http2",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.opentelemetry]
version = "0.22.0"
features = [ "trace", "metrics",]

[dependencies.rustls]
optional = true
version = "0.22.2"

[dependencies.rustls-platform-verifier]
optional = true
version = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.196"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.112"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.thiserror]
version = "1.0.57"

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = [ "util",]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4.4"
features = [ "cors",]

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.tracing-opentelemetry]
version = "0.23.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.mas-tower]
optional = true
path = "./crates/tower/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dev-dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1.0.79"

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.35.1"
features = [ "macros", "rt",]

[package]
name = "mas-iana"
description = "IANA registry data for JOSE and OAuth 2.0"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Quentin Gliech <quenting@element.io>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0"
homepage = "https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-authentication-service/"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service/"

[features]
default = [ "serde", "schemars",]
serde = [ "dep:serde",]
schemars = [ "dep:schemars",]

[lints.rust]
unsafe_code = "forbid"

[lints.clippy]
all = "deny"
pedantic = "warn"
str_to_string = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "deny"

[dependencies.serde]
optional = true
version = "1.0.196"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.schemars]
optional = true
version = "0.8.16"
features = [ "url", "chrono", "preserve_order",]

[package]
name = "mas-jose"
description = "JSON Object Signing and Encryption (JWT & co) utilities"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Quentin Gliech <quenting@element.io>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0"
homepage = "https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-authentication-service/"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service/"

[dependencies]
digest = "0.10.7"
elliptic-curve = "0.13.8"
generic-array = "0.14.7"
hmac = "0.12.1"
rsa = "0.9.6"
sec1 = "0.7.3"
serde_with = "3.7.0"
signature = "2.2.0"

[dev-dependencies]
rand_chacha = "0.3.1"

[lints.rust]
unsafe_code = "forbid"

[lints.clippy]
all = "deny"
pedantic = "warn"
str_to_string = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "deny"

[dependencies.base64ct]
version = "1.6.0"
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.35"
default-features = false
features = [ "serde", "clock",]

[dependencies.ecdsa]
version = "0.16.9"
features = [ "signing", "verifying",]

[dependencies.k256]
version = "0.13.3"
features = [ "ecdsa",]

[dependencies.p256]
version = "0.13.2"
features = [ "ecdsa",]

[dependencies.p384]
version = "0.13.0"
features = [ "ecdsa",]

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.schemars]
version = "0.8.16"
features = [ "url", "chrono", "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.196"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.112"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.sha2]
version = "0.10.8"
features = [ "oid",]

[dependencies.thiserror]
version = "1.0.57"

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.5.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.mas-iana]
path = "./crates/iana/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dev-dependencies.insta]
version = "1.34.0"

[package]
name = "mas-oidc-client"
description = "OpenID Connect client library used by the Matrix Authentication Service"
version = "0.8.0"
authors = [ "Quentin Gliech <quenting@element.io>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "Apache-2.0"
homepage = "https://matrix-org.github.io/matrix-authentication-service/"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service/"

[features]
default = [ "hyper", "keystore",]
hyper = [ "dep:http-body", "dep:hyper", "dep:hyper-rustls", "dep:rustls", "dep:rustls-platform-verifier", "dep:tower-http", "tower/limit",]
keystore = [ "dep:mas-keystore",]

[dependencies]
bytes = "1.5.0"
form_urlencoded = "1.2.1"
futures-util = "0.3.30"
headers = "0.3.9"
language-tags = "0.3.2"
mime = "0.3.17"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
serde_with = "3.7.0"

[dev-dependencies]
assert_matches = "1.5.0"
bitflags = "2.4.2"
rand_chacha = "0.3.1"
wiremock = "0.5.22"

[lints.rust]
unsafe_code = "forbid"

[lints.clippy]
all = "deny"
pedantic = "warn"
str_to_string = "deny"

[lints.rustdoc]
broken_intra_doc_links = "deny"

[dependencies.base64ct]
version = "1.6.0"
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.35"
default-features = false
features = [ "serde", "clock",]

[dependencies.http]
version = "0.2.11"

[dependencies.rand]
version = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.196"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.112"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.thiserror]
version = "1.0.57"

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = [ "util",]

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.40"

[dependencies.url]
version = "2.5.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.mas-http]
path = "./crates/http/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dependencies.mas-iana]
path = "./crates/iana/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dependencies.mas-jose]
path = "./crates/jose/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dependencies.mas-keystore]
optional = true
path = "./crates/keystore/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dependencies.oauth2-types]
path = "./crates/oauth2-types/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dependencies.http-body]
version = "0.4.5"
optional = true

[dependencies.rustls]
optional = true
version = "0.22.2"

[dependencies.rustls-platform-verifier]
optional = true
version = "0.2.0"

[dependencies.hyper-rustls]
optional = true
version = "0.25.0"
features = [ "http1", "http2",]
default-features = false

[dependencies.hyper]
version = "0.14.27"
features = [ "client", "http1", "http2", "stream", "runtime",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4.4"
features = [ "follow-redirect", "set-header", "timeout", "map-request-body", "util",]
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.mas-keystore]
path = "./crates/keystore/"
version = "=0.8.0"

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.35.1"
features = [ "rt", "macros", "rt-multi-thread",]

[[test]]
name = "integration"
required-features = [ "testing",]

[package]
authors = [ "Damir Jelić <poljar@termina.org.uk>",]
description = "A high level Matrix client-server library."
edition = "2021"
homepage = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
keywords = [ "matrix", "chat", "messaging", "ruma", "nio",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
name = "matrix-sdk"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
rust-version = "1.76"
version = "0.7.1"

[features]
default = [ "e2e-encryption", "automatic-room-key-forwarding", "sqlite", "native-tls",]
testing = [ "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/testing", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/testing", "matrix-sdk-base/testing", "wiremock",]
e2e-encryption = [ "matrix-sdk-base/e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/message-ids", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/crypto-store", "matrix-sdk-indexeddb?/e2e-encryption",]
js = [ "matrix-sdk-common/js", "matrix-sdk-base/js",]
sqlite = [ "dep:matrix-sdk-sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/state-store",]
bundled-sqlite = [ "sqlite", "matrix-sdk-sqlite?/bundled",]
indexeddb = [ "matrix-sdk-indexeddb/state-store",]
qrcode = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/qrcode",]
automatic-room-key-forwarding = [ "e2e-encryption", "matrix-sdk-base/automatic-room-key-forwarding",]
markdown = [ "ruma/markdown",]
native-tls = [ "reqwest/native-tls",]
rustls-tls = [ "reqwest/rustls-tls",]
socks = [ "reqwest/socks",]
sso-login = [ "dep:hyper", "dep:rand", "dep:tower",]
image-proc = [ "dep:image",]
image-rayon = [ "image-proc", "image?/jpeg_rayon",]
uniffi = [ "dep:uniffi",]
experimental-oidc = [ "ruma/unstable-msc2967", "dep:chrono", "dep:language-tags", "dep:mas-oidc-client", "dep:rand", "dep:sha2", "dep:tower",]
experimental-sliding-sync = [ "matrix-sdk-base/experimental-sliding-sync", "reqwest/gzip", "dep:eyeball-im-util",]
experimental-widgets = [ "dep:language-tags", "dep:uuid",]
docsrs = [ "e2e-encryption", "sqlite", "indexeddb", "sso-login", "qrcode", "image-proc",]

[dependencies]
anymap2 = "0.13.0"
aquamarine = "0.5.0"
as_variant = "1.2.0"
async-channel = "2.1.0"
async-stream = "0.3.3"
async-trait = "0.1.60"
bytes = "1.1.0"
bytesize = "1.1"
cfg-vis = "0.3.0"
event-listener = "4.0.0"
futures-core = "0.3.28"
http = "0.2.6"
indexmap = "2.0.2"
js_int = "0.2.2"
mime = "0.3.16"
mime2ext = "0.1.52"
serde = "1.0.151"
serde_html_form = "0.2.0"
serde_json = "1.0.91"
tempfile = "3.3.0"
thiserror = "1.0.38"
url = "2.2.2"
urlencoding = "2.1.3"
zeroize = "1.6.0"

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.68"
assert-json-diff = "2"
assert_matches = "1.5.0"
assert_matches2 = "0.1.1"
dirs = "5.0.1"
futures-executor = "0.3.21"
once_cell = "1.16.0"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
stream_assert = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.anyhow]
optional = true
version = "1.0.68"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.23"
optional = true

[dependencies.eyeball]
version = "0.8.7"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyeball-im]
version = "0.4.1"
features = [ "tracing",]

[dependencies.eyeball-im-util]
optional = true
version = "0.5.1"

[dependencies.eyre]
version = "0.6.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.hyper]

[dependencies.imbl]

version = "2.0.0"

[dependencies.language-tags]

[dependencies.mas-oidc-client]

rev = "099eabd1371d2840a2f025a6372d6428039eb511"
default-features = false
optional = true

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
features = [ "uniffi",]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-common]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-common"
version = "0.7.0"

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-indexeddb]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-indexeddb"
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.matrix-sdk-sqlite]
optional = true
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-sqlite"
version = "0.7.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rand]
optional = true
version = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.ruma]
features = [ "client-api-c", "compat-upload-signatures", "compat-user-id", "compat-arbitrary-length-ids", "compat-tag-info", "unstable-msc3401",]
git = "https://github.com/ruma/ruma"
rev = "4c00bd010dbdca6005bd599b52e90a0b7015d056"

[dependencies.sha2]
optional = true
version = "0.10.8"

[dependencies.tokio-stream]
features = [ "sync",]
version = "0.1.14"

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.4.13"
features = [ "make",]
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing]
features = [ "std",]
version = "0.1.40"
default-features = false

[dependencies.uniffi]
optional = true
git = "https://github.com/mozilla/uniffi-rs"
rev = "789a9023b522562a95618443cee5a0d4f111c4c7"

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1.4.1"
features = [ "serde", "v4",]
optional = true

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.24.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "gif", "jpeg", "ico", "png", "pnm", "tga", "tiff", "webp", "bmp", "hdr", "dxt", "dds", "farbfeld",]
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-base]
features = [ "testing",]
path = "crates/matrix-sdk-base"
version = "0.7.0"

[dev-dependencies.matrix-sdk-test]
path = "testing/matrix-sdk-test"
version = "0.7.0"

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.11"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3.33"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
tokio-util = "0.7.9"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "docsrs",]
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.gloo-timers]
version = "0.3.0"
features = [ "futures",]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.10"
default_features = false

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.30.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "sync",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.backoff]
version = "0.4.0"
features = [ "tokio",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.reqwest]

default_features = false
features = [ "stream",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.tokio]
features = [ "sync",]
version = "1.30.0"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies.wiremock]
optional = true
version = "0.5.21"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.tokio]
workspace = true
features = [ "rt-multi-thread", "macros",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies.wiremock]
version = "0.5.13"

authors = [ "Damir Jelić <poljar@termina.org.uk>", "Denis Kasak <dkasak@termina.org.uk>",]
name = "vodozemac"
description = "A Rust implementation of Olm and Megolm"
repository = "https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac"
version = "0.5.1"
edition = "2021"
keywords = [ "matrix", "chat", "messaging", "olm",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
rust-version = "1.65"

[features]
default = [ "libolm-compat",]
js = [ "getrandom/js",]
strict-signatures = []
libolm-compat = []
low-level-api = []

[dependencies]
aes = "0.8.4"
base64 = "0.22.0"
getrandom = "0.2.12"
hkdf = "0.12.4"
hmac = "0.12.1"
pkcs7 = "0.4.1"
prost = "0.12.3"
rand = "0.8.5"
serde_bytes = "0.11.14"
serde_json = "1.0.114"
sha2 = "0.10.8"
subtle = "2.5.0"
thiserror = "1.0.58"
zeroize = "1.7.0"

[dev-dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.81"
assert_matches = "1.5.0"
olm-rs = "2.2.0"
proptest = "1.4.0"

[dependencies.arrayvec]
version = "0.7.4"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.cbc]
version = "0.1.2"
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.curve25519-dalek]
version = "4.1.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "zeroize",]

[dependencies.ed25519-dalek]
version = "2.1.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "rand_core", "std", "serde", "hazmat", "zeroize",]

[dependencies.matrix-pickle]
version = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.197"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.x25519-dalek]
version = "2.0.1"
features = [ "serde", "reusable_secrets", "static_secrets", "zeroize",]

[patch.crates-io.olm-rs]
git = "https://github.com/poljar/olm-rs"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service"]
git = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-authentication-service"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "099eabd1371d2840a2f025a6372d6428039eb511"

[source."https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"]
git = "https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-rust-sdk"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "ab9e4f73b1b43e0779080b714e0916496a052cc3"

[source."https://github.com/ruma/ruma"]
git = "https://github.com/ruma/ruma"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "4c00bd010dbdca6005bd599b52e90a0b7015d056"

[source."https://github.com/mozilla/uniffi-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/mozilla/uniffi-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "789a9023b522562a95618443cee5a0d4f111c4c7"

[source."https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac"]
git = "https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "0c75746fc8a5eda4a0e490d345d1798b4c6cbd67"
